@SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress = http://localhost:2805

### 要求 Outlook folders，Request Outlook folders
POST {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/request-folders
Accept: application/json

### 以 Outlook Add-in 身分 poll 下一筆 command
GET {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/poll
Accept: application/json

### 從 Outlook Add-in push folders
POST {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/push-folders
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "name": "Mailbox",
    "folderPath": "\\\\Mailbox",
    "itemCount": 0,
    "subFolders": [
      {
        "name": "Inbox",
        "folderPath": "\\\\Mailbox\\\\Inbox",
        "itemCount": 3,
        "subFolders": []
      }
    ]
  }
]

### 要求 Outlook mails，Request Outlook mails
POST {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/request-mails
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "folderPath": "\\\\Mailbox\\\\Inbox",
  "range": "1d",
  "maxCount": 10
}

### 取得 cached mails
GET {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/mails
Accept: application/json

### 送出 chat message
POST {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "web",
  "text": "請摘要選取的 mails。"
}

### 取得 Add-in status
GET {{SmartOffice.Hub_HostAddress}}/api/outlook/admin/status
Accept: application/json
